    • Field Detail

      • resByTable

        private java.util.HashMap<java.lang.Integer,​java.util.ArrayList<Reservation>> resByTable
        a collection of all reservations using HashMap. The HashMap stores table id and an ArrayList of reservations at that table

      • allReservations

        private java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​Reservation> allReservations
        a collection of all reservations using HashMap. The HashMap stores reservation key and Reservation object pair. The reservation key is a concatenated string of name + contact number + reservation date of the reservation

      • scheduler

        private static java.util.concurrent.ScheduledExecutorService scheduler
        a scheduler to schedule auto remove events to remove reservations upon expiry (15 minutes after reservation time)

    • Method Detail

      • restoreAutoRemove

        public void restoreAutoRemove()
        Restore all the auto cancel events. All auto cancel events of reservations are not stored since the delay time passed to scheduler to schedule the event depends on runtime. Hence, this is to be called when the restaurant is restored. It also clears all reservations that expired when the system is closed

      • initTableReservation

        public void initTableReservation​(int tableID)
        Initialise a new entry of table ID and an ArrayList to store all reservations made at this table in HashMap resByTable. It is called when a new Table is created
        Parameters:
        tableID - new table ID

      • checkAvail

        public java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.Integer> checkAvail​(java.time.LocalDateTime time)
        Check each table's availability at given time by checking reservations at that table, return an ArrayList of table IDs that can be allocated after checking reservations
        The condition is there are no reservations are 2 hours before and after the the given time, since we assume the table will be vacated 2 hours after the customers start dining
        - e.g. if the given time is 5pm, then the condition is satisfied if there are no reservations from 3pm to 7pm
        Parameters:
        time - time given to check table's availability
        Returns:
        an ArrayList of available table IDs

        Parameters:

        Returns:
